    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable, well-loved, and still looks great on the road! I\u2019ve kept up with the maintenance, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road for its next adventure with you. It\u2019s the perfect balance of comfort and dependability. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
