    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies. The VANOS unit has been professionally serviced and rod bearings addressed, ensuring long-term reliability of the valvetrain and bottom end. Power is routed through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock. The suspension has been optimized with Bilstein coilovers and the rear subframe\u2014a known weak point\u2014has been reinforced for structural rigidity. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain remains tight with consistent compression across all cylinders. It is a driver-spec machine tuned for communicative feedback and peak lateral performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
