    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents the perfect balance of luxury and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side alloy wheel\u2014honest signs of a car that has enjoyed the open road. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the supple leather seats have been treated regularly and show only light bolster wear on the driver's side. All electronic systems, from the premium surround-sound audio to the intuitive navigation interface, function exactly as they did the day it left the showroom. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, with a thick folder of receipts to prove it. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are imperceptible, and the tires have approximately 70% tread remaining. This is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle that has been garaged nightly, offering the next owner a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 34800.0,
